room_title: Escape room "Vacation Vandals" by Key Quest in Los Angeles
room_description: Your dream vacation is booked. Your bags are packed and all that is left is a quick stop by the travel agency to pick up your tickets. When you pull into the parking lot, you can see the front door to the travel agency has been smashed. Cautiously you enter the room only to find the infamous Vacation Vandals have ransacked the office. Find your tickets and you will still have time to make it to the airport!
